OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy with rain likely in the west,
OL,7,Fespecially across the Pennines, more
OL,8,Fsettled and drier in the east. The
OL,9,Fwind is expected to gradually ease
OL,10,Fovernight and become less gusty.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy and breezy for most
OL,13,Fwith spells of rain affecting many
OL,14,Fplaces. Heavier and more persistent
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain likely across
OL,16,Fwestern hills. Temperatures around or
OL,17,Fslightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
