OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fand Tuesday, cloudy with spells of
OL,7,Frain at times, mostly affecting
OL,8,Fwestern hills with drier conditions
OL,9,Ffurther east. Wednesday becoming drier
OL,10,Fand sunnier. Temperatures becoming
OL,11,Frather warm.
